	* keylist.c (list_cert_colon): Avoid duplicate listing of kludge
	uids.

	* verify.c (gpgsm_verify): Make STATUS_VERIFY return the hash and
	pk algo.
	* certcheck.c (gpgsm_check_cms_signature): Add arg R_PKALGO.

