	* gpgsm.c (set_debug): Changed to use a globals DEBUG_LEVEL and
	DEBUG_VALUE.
	(main): Made DEBUG_LEVEL global and introduced DEBUG_VALUE.  This
	now allows to add debug flags on top of a debug-level setting.

